<a href="http://www.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=19453" target="_blank" class="postlink">Charm of Deception </a> drops from the Mines of Torrigan side of the Crypt of Nadox. The mob the drops it <a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=11184" target="_blank" class="postlink">Karsonizzak Bloodblade</a> is lvl 52. There is plenty of room in this area to fear kite the mobs. Beauty of this charm is that it gives its benifits when you are not in your true form, ie. Lich mode. This was my first charm and I held it till I got my PoP charm.<br />_________________<br />Cathain Corpsemaster</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
