			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Go to nadox and lessor succor will bring you to the ZL to the mines.
<br />
From there clear your way to the Shrine and kill everything there for a few hours and you'll get this
<br />

<br />
Charm of Deception
<br />

<br />
Drops of the Annoying Name dude that keep poping up all the time, killed him Soo many time there can't remember. And if you bring a few caster with ya (you can use MW, non stop) cause there is caster all over the place inthere. At 65 even CoB with not have any problem to kill there. These caster are pretty much wimps. Best in duo with someone so you can just concentrate on DPS but doable solo.
<br />

<br />
Oh if you manage to pop the Shrine even ... well then might wanna get a few friends BEFORE starting the killing. Cause you'll start poping wave of mobs and once you get the one that pop like 12 of em, then they will despan and you lose the even, so if you see some Untargetable mobs poped in ... bring a chanter and some friends ... and do the event !!!
<br />

<br />

<br />
Anyway .. the charm DO drop there and it seem to be a RARE drop off that guy (killed him like 30 times) and got only one drop ... so ..
<br />

<br />

<br />
Good luck<br />_________________<br /><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: normal"><span style="color: darkred">Virun Waulfebane</span></span>
<br />
<span style="color: red">Adept Vampire</span>
<br />

<br />
